  RFC2980 [label="RFC2980
Common NNTP Extensions
2000", shape=ellipse, fillcolor="#e8f0ff", tooltip="In this document, a number of popular extensions to the Network News Transfer Protocol (NNTP) protocol defined in RFC 977 are documented and discussed.  While this document is not intended to serve as a standard of any kind, it will hopefully serve as a reference document for future implementers of the NNTP protocol.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.", style=filled, fillcolor=green]; 

